  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1655790/" class="title-link">巫术的一般理论写作路径</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1655790"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/penglai59/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2748388-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/penglai59/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">剪</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-02-05"
      class="main-meta">2009-02-05 16:03:28</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1655790_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                      莫斯意在为人类的个体行为寻找社会的、集体的根源，他极力把巫术从个体心理探源引向社会事实研究（典型的社会学年鉴派研究方法）。     他的研究思路有特色：先区别宗教与巫术，给巫术下一个宽泛的定义“跟任何有组织的教派无关的仪式都是巫术仪式”，这种不以仪式结构，而...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1655790/#comments">(4回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">7有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_1655790_full" class="hidden">
